/*\n  # Remove Unique Constraint from Prize_Instantprizes Table\n\n  1. Changes\n    - Remove the unique constraint on `competitionId` column in `Prize_Instantprizes` table\n    - This allows multiple instant win prizes to be associated with the same competition\n    - Each prize winner will have their own unique record with their own winning ticket number\n\n  2. Reasoning\n    - Instant win competitions can have multiple winners\n    - Each winner needs a separate entry with their unique winning ticket number\n    - The UID field remains unique to identify each individual prize win\n*/\n\nALTER TABLE "Prize_Instantprizes" \nDROP CONSTRAINT IF EXISTS "Prize_Instantprizes_competitionId_key";
;
